籤詩版本二:
Kunzima kakhulu ukulwela impumelelo, kodwa izinsuku zokulwela umshado zimatasa okwesikhashana.
Ekugcineni uyoshaywa umcibisholo, umnumzane uqondise abantu abakhulu.
詩意:
Le hexagram imele isibusiso esifihlekile.
Konke kuhle.
解曰: Ushintsho lwamabomu. U-Enron ekugcineni. Uma ubuza mayelana nokusetshenziswa. Kuphela eduze nabantu abahloniphekile.
籤詩故事一:
◇Isincomo sencwadi i-Jiang Wei (Isincomo sencwadi i-Jiang Wei)
UJiang Wei (202-264), igama lokuhlonipha u-Boyue, wayengowokuzalwa eSifundazweni saseJi, eSifundazweni saseTianshui, eLiangzhou (manje esesiFundazweni saseGangu, iDolobha laseTianshui, esifundazweni saseGansu).
Ngesikhathi seMibuso Emithathu, u-Kong Ming wahola amasosha akhe esuka e-Qishan Mountain izikhathi eziyisithupha eyohlasela i-Cao Wei. U-Kong Ming wayegula kakhulu futhi esesimweni esibucayi. Ufundise izahluko ezingamashumi amabili nane zeNcwadi Yempi kujenene uJiang Wei, ngethemba lokuthi angazuza ifa lakhe.
(Isingathekiso sale ndaba ukuthi uJiang Wei wazuzwa ngesizathu esithile)
聖意: Inhlanhla yomndeni, inhlanhla, ibhizinisi, umshado, uLiujia, abahamba ngezinyawo besilisa abakafiki, Tiansi Zhongping, Liu izilwane ezifuywayo, Zhongping, ufuna abantu, amacala omphakathi, ukufuduka okufanelekile, impahla elahlekile, izifo zaseMpumalanga, ithuna le-Xingxingshan elihle
古人: Izincomo zencwadi eziya ku-Jiang Wei (Izincwadi eziya ku-Jiang Wei)
